* * *

libgcp is a free implementation of GCP, a protocol for enabling simple
message passing over a serial network.

For the full protocol specification, see gcp-spec.pdf in the doc
directory.

For a quick guide on using libgcp, see prog-guide.pdf in the doc
directory.

For the full reference manual, see refman.pdf in the doc directory.
